### Page Structure Requirements

#### 1. Essential Pages Only
- **Home/Dashboard**: Main application interface
- **Login**: User authentication
- **User Management**: User administration (if applicable)
- **Settings**: Application configuration (if applicable)

#### 2. Page Layout
