### Common Issues to Avoid

#### Design Issues
- Using bright, flashy colors
- Implementing complex gradients
- Over-animating elements
- Inconsistent spacing
- Poor typography choices

#### UX Issues
- Confusing navigation
- Unclear user flows
- Poor mobile experience
- Slow loading times
- Inaccessible design